eferred hard and soft skills. Example Billing Specialist requirements High school education or GED Problem solving abilities to handle customers Microsoft Excel expert Strong organizational skills to keep track of everything 2-3 years of experience in billing Ability to work independently Billing Specialist related job titles: Billing Manager Billing Officer Billing Associate Business Clerk Office Clerk Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
